# Probabilistic German Morphosyntax
# Roland Schäfer, Freie Universität Berlin

with contributions from Ulrike Sayatz and Elizabeth Pankratz

The papers collected and enhanced here as well as the introductory part of
the book form my "kumulative Habilitation". The paper on sequences of oblique
attributive adjectives was added later.


TECHNICAL NOTES

* The Inconsolata-g font can be obtained here: http://www.fantascienza.net/leonardo/ar/inconsolatag/inconsolata-g_font.zip

* Inconsolata-g installation on Ubuntu:

> sudo mkdir /usr/share/fonts/truetype/customfonts
> sudo cp Inconsolatar.ttf /usr/share/fonts/truetype/customfonts/
> sudo fc-cache -fv
